cling and waste collections"],"\n",["P",{},"On your scheduled collection day, please make sure your containers are at your collection point by ",["STRONG",{},"6:30am"],". We may collect your containers at any time on your collection day up until ",["STRONG",{},"5pm"],", so please leave your containers out until then. "],"\n",["H3",{},"Missed refuse collections"],"\n",["P",{},["STRONG",{},"Please do not report a missed refuse collection until after 5pm on your collection day as our crews may still be out collecting up until this time"],". ",["A",{"class":"sys_0 sys_t0","href":"/en/bins-and-recycling/report-a-missed-refuse-collection.aspx"},"Find out more about missed refuse collections"],"."],"\n"],"\n\n",["P",{},"You can find out your collection dates by entering your address details into the search box below."],"\n",["P",{},"Bin collections don't change on bank holidays except Christmas Day, Boxing Day and New Year's Day."],"\n",["H2",{},"When are my bin collection dates?"],"\n","\n",["P",{},"To find your next bin collection day, please enter your postcode in the search box below and click ",["STRONG",{},"\"View bin collections\""],". "],"\n\n\n",["DIV",{"class":"bin-collection-dates-webaspx bin-collection-dates-iframe-june-2024"},"\n    ",["IFRAME",{"__playwright_bounding_rect__":"{\"left\":15,\"top\":1040.890625,\"right\":746.5,\"bottom\":1740.890625}","src":"/snapshot/frame@0fbba55a1b5369f47efa32716c98c6b7","title":"Bin collection dates"}],"\n"],"\n","\n",["H2",{},["A",{"id":"WhattimeshouldIputmybinsout"},"What time should I put my bins out?"]],"\n",["P",{},["STRONG",{},"Your bins should be placed on the kerbside by 6:30am."]],"\n",["P",{},"If you do not place your containers out for collection before 6:30am or put your containers out on the wrong day, you'll need to either: "],"\n",["UL",{},"\n",["LI",{},"wait for your next scheduled collection"],"\n",["LI",{},"take your recycling and non-recyclable waste to your ",["A",{"class":"sys_0 sys_t0","href":"/en/bins-and-recycling/waste-parks/recycling-and-waste-disposal.aspx"},"local Waste and Recycling Park"]],"\n"],"\n",["P",{},"If you have placed your bin out for collection and it has not been emptied, please check to see if there is a contamination tag or sticker on your bin. If there is, we will not return to empty your bin."],"\n",["P",{},"Please note that we keep a record of bins that have not been presented and that are contaminated."],"\n",["P",{},"In the case that you believe our crew have accidently missed your bin, ",["A",{"class":"sys_0 sys_t0","href":"/en/bins-and-recycling/report-a-missed-refuse-collection.aspx"},"you can report a missed collection online"],"."],"\n"],"\n"],"\n"],"\n\n"],"\n"],"\n\n",["FOOTER",{"role":"contentinfo"},"\n",["DIV",{"class":"grid-container grid-container-padded"},"\n",["DIV",{"class":"grid-x grid-margin-x align-top"},"\n",["DIV",{"class":"cell small-12 medium-12 large-12"},["UL",{"class":"menu footer-links-row-01"},"\n  ",["LI",{},["A",{"id":"footer-links","accesskey":"0","href":"/en/website/website-accessibility/website-accessibility.aspx"},"Accessibility"]],"\n  ",["LI",{},["A",{"accesskey":"9","href":"/en/contact-us/contact-us.aspx"},"Contact"]],"\n  ",["LI",{},["A",{"href":"/en/website/cookies/cookies.aspx"},"Cookies"]],"\n  ",["LI",{},["A",{"href":"/en/emergencies/emergencies.aspx"},"Emergencies"]],"\n  ",["LI",{},["A",{"href":"/en/privacy/privacy.aspx"},"Privacy"]],"\n  ",["LI",{},["A",{"accesskey":"3","href":"/en/website/site-map.aspx"},"Site map"]],"\n  ",["LI",{},["A",{"accesskey":"8","href":"/en/website/terms-and-conditions.aspx"},"Terms and conditions"]],"\n\n"],"\n",["UL",{"class":"menu footer-links-row-02"},"\n ",["LI",{},["A",{"class":"footer-social-facebook","href":"http://www.facebook.com/denbighshirecountycouncil"},"Facebook"]],"\n ",["LI",{},["A",{"class":"footer-social-instagram","href":"https://www.instagram.com/denbighshirecc/"},"Instagram"]],"\n ",["LI",{},["A",{"class":"footer-social-linkedin","href":"https://w